<!--
* Transforming files
*******************************************************
* How to add a transformer from the file namespace to a message flow
* Transformer will allow us to convert the payload of our message from a file to a string.
* pick the file from the file system (inbound channel adapter), send it to the inbound channel
 the inbound channel delivers it to the transformer, the transformer transforms the file to a string and
 places it to the transformChannel and the channel drops it to the service activator which sends the message
 to the FilePrinter  where the contents of the file will be printed.
-->
